:: Wraith Snatched Gwylan Fight Finish
<<effects>><<getTarget true>>
<<if $control gte $controlmax>>
	<<wraithExorcise true true>><<clearWraith>><<endWraith>>
	<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
	<span class="gold">You stop.</span> You can feel it pushing you to keep going, to keep fighting, but you dig your heels in and focus. You have your body back, and you don't plan on giving it up.
	<br><br>

	<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
		<b>"<span class="witch">Sit!</span>"</b>
		<br><br>

		<<hypnosisText "<span class='blue'>You can't resist that, though. Your body collapses.</span>">> Gwylan quickly kneels next to you, pulling a vial from <<his>> belt. <<He>> rips the cork out, and holds it under your nose.
		<br><br>

		You tremble. All at once, the Wraith is pulled out of your body from above. It dissipates into nothingness with a brief shriek that echoes in your mind. Your ears ring, and you hear its voice all around you.
	<<else>>
		You double over in agony. It's pulling itself out of you, knowing it's been bested. You see a pair of pale, translucent arms erupt from your chest. With a great amount of effort, it expels itself out of you.
		<br><br>

		Its head snaps back, and it dissipates into nothingness with a brief shriek that echoes in your mind. Your ears ring, and you hear its voice all around you.
	<</if>>
	<<if $wraith.state is "haunt">>
		"<span class="wraith">The albatross around your throat will drag you to the bottom.</span>"
	<<else>>
		"<span class="wraith">The fox snatches the albatross from the wind.</span>"
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>
		Gwylan huffs as the figure disappears.
	<<else>>
		Gwylan huffs as the <<print Weather.precipitation>> begins to clear up.
	<</if>>
	"I'm sorry, but I won't let you have <<phim>>." <<He>> looks back to you. "You're a troublesome one, you know that?" <<He>> hugs you tightly.
	<br><br>

	<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
		"Why didn't you lead with that?" you ask, hugging back.
		<br><br>

		"It had too much control, and the mixture wasn't what freed you. That just made the exit more clean." <<He>> smiles.
	<</if>>
	"Come on. I'll make you some tea back at the shop."
	<br><br>

	You're in no position to resist.
	<<if $pain gte 75>>
		Gwylan puts one of your arms around <<him>> and helps you walk.
	<</if>>
	It isn't a long trip to the shop.

	<<endcombat>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Forest Shop Wraith Talk Repeat]]>><<clotheson>><<set $forest to 0>><</link>>
<<else>>
	Gwylan falls to the ground. You fall on top of <<him>>, your hands around <<his>> throat. "<span class="wraith">The fox plays the part of the prey.</span>"
	<br><br>

	<<He>> can't breathe. <<His>> hands grip your wrists, but <<he>> can't pull them away. <<He>> reaches for something on <<his>> belt, but it's smacked away by another arm.
	<br><br>

	<span class="red"><<His>> struggling becomes weaker and weaker, <<his>> eyes becoming more dim. <<He>> releases you, <<his>> arms falling limp at <<his>> sides.</span>
	<br><br>

	"<span class="wraith">Alas. Your torment was never mine to end.</span>"
	<br><br>

	You release <<him>>, and <<he>> gasps for breath. <<He>> coughs as you stand. "<span class="wraith">Hie away, witch. Suffer alone in your self-made cage.</span>"
	<br><br>

	You start to walk away, but <<he>> grabs your ankle.
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners") and C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 135>>
		<<gwylanRescueStats true "WraithFight">>
		<<silently>><<endcombat>><</silently>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
		"You..." <<he>> gasps, <<his>> breath ragged and hoarse. "...can't have <<phim>>." <<He>> drags <<himself>> forwards. You look down in bemusement. "Nobody can."
		<br><br>

		<span class="nextLink"><<link [[Next|Wraith Snatched Gwylan Fight Finish Nobody]]>><</link>></span>
	<<else>>
		<<gwylanRescueStats false "WraithFight">>
		<<His>> grip is weak and desperate. You kick it aside without effort.
		<br><br>

		You leave Gwylan weak and breathless in the clearing.
		<<endcombat>>
		<br><br>

		<span class="nextLink"><<exitWraith true>></span>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

:: Wraith Snatched Gwylan Fight Finish Nobody
<<canvas-model-freeze "precipitation">>
<span class="red">A whale sings a mournful song for its lost pod. A fox cries out for its kits. An albatross crashes to the sand with broken wings. A serpent sheds its skin, before devouring its own eggs.</span>
The sky screams in anguish, before everything goes completely silent. <<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>The <<print Weather.precipitation>> freezes in the air.<</if>>
<br><br>

Nobody is here.
<br><br>

Nobody stands up.
<br><br>

Nobody's sharp, blackened fingers pierce through your chest. You feel nothing.
<br><br>

Nobody screams, antlers ablaze in red moonlight. All is silent.
<br><br>

Nobody rips the intruder from your body.
<br><br>

Nobody, and the Wraith, fade away in a torrent of water and rose petals.
<br><br>

